{"tid":2257960,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"麥路人口碑差到大陸網買完版權都唔收錢畀人任睇","createTime":"2020-10-25T15:44:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-10T20:42:57.000Z","uid":39360,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e76e9ad8eabe8506753ed8d9a7c6ec813152822d","tid":2257960,"uid":39360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T15:44:36.000Z","msg":"聽講正常新戲擺大陸愛奇藝（我估係類似Netflix 果類平台掛？），除咗畀十幾蚊月費做會員仲要畀幾蚊先睇到（據說係睇口碑之類，Marvel新戲直頭要畀多廿蚊，舊/爛戲多數做會員就直接免費）<br />\n<br />\n但近排人瑞唔知咩事連大陸Fans都勁反佢<br />\n（好似話佢冇歌藝呃飯食、肥、醜樣、個飲食節目買點擊率之類，總之就一連串野加埋關公災難啦）<br />\n<br />\n套戲喺大陸仆晒街，連愛奇藝都淨係做會員就睇得，直接歸類去同舊戲/爛戲一個level...<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W95Xnxn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW95Xnxn.png&h=e5caa0ae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"78c9acd196c0b9a1b148798f74b1840a7f982825","tid":2257960,"uid":201027,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T15:45:57.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"pink\">抵撚死</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n等睇奶共千女华變票房毒藥"},{"pid":"4317888c76e1ec9dff871b1fa58e168510ca1e21","tid":2257960,"uid":39360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-25T15:48:05.000Z","msg":"補多張圖<br />\n正常新戲會好似圖入面果啲咁一係呃你買vip一係好似RDJ果套咁要另外收錢<br />\n而麥路人係冇呢兩個icon直接任睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3gBGPif.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3gBGPif.png&h=f06f3c27&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1de94e669232263074978dc2d4502f2af5b2b2d2","tid":2257960,"uid":183058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T10:56:25.000Z","msg":"麥路人 豆瓣6.6可以了，想打擊人瑞，要真憑實據才行。<br />\n大陸文青對華語片都十分苛刻，6分以上已經及格了。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.douban.com/doubanapp/dispatch/movie/30312137\" data-sr-u